  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Kikwiflow平台画一个架构图，展示它是如何嵌入到用户的Spring Boot应用中的。核心要体现三个层次：用户的应用层、Kikwiflow平台层，还有数据层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sua Aplicação (Spring Boot)",
        "Plataforma Kikwiflow (Embarcada)",
        "Camada de Dados (Pluggable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。用户应用层里具体要放哪些组件？我看到有UserCode和KikwiRestApi这两个概念，它们是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "UserCode代表用户的业务代码，比如Controllers和Services；KikwiRestApi是一个可选的管理API。两者都是用户应用的一部分，但功能不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把用户应用层画成左到右的布局，包含这两个组件。现在来看Kikwiflow平台层，这里写着\"Embarcada\"，是要强调嵌入式特性吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plataforma Kikwiflow (Embarcada)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，平台是嵌入式的。这一层内部要用CQRS模式，分成命令端和查询端。命令端是Motor de Comando，查询端是Serviço de Consulta。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Orquestração e Consulta (CQRS)",
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CQRS我理解了。平台层还有另一个子图叫\"Pontos de Extensão\"，这里的\"Lógica Segura\"是什么意思？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pontos de Extensão (Lógica Segura)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是安全扩展点，用户可以通过Regras de Negócio和Automações来扩展平台行为，但不会影响核心引擎的稳定性。Regras对应DecisionRule，Automações对应JavaDelegate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rules",
        "Delegates",
        "DecisionRule",
        "JavaDelegate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "平台层画好了，两个子图：CQRS和扩展点。现在数据层标注为\"Pluggable\"，是要表达存储可插拔？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Camada de Dados (Pluggable)",
        "Persistence"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Persistence支持InMemory、MongoDB等多种实现，用户可以根据环境选择。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Persistence",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "三层结构清楚了。现在来画连接关系：UserCode应该同时连到CommandEngine和QueryService吧？因为业务代码既要发命令也要查状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，双向连接。KikwiRestApi作为管理API，同样要连到这两个端点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "KikwiRestApi",
        "CommandEngine",
        "QueryService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
